public class DateAndTimeFormatSynonymGenerator extends SynonymGenerator<SimpleDateFormat,net.sf.jsqlparser.expression.Expression>
SynonymGenerator for dateformats, timeformats and datetimeformats. Needs SimpleDateFormat and Expression as type.
